Insider Activity


Individual




Wei Sun Christianson



Ms. Wei Sun Christianson is Independent Director at Estee Lauder Cos., Inc. , Co-Chief Executive Officer & Managing Director at Morgan Stanley Asia Ltd., and Chief Executive Officer at Morgan Stanley Asia Ltd.(China). She is on the Board of Directors at Estee Lauder Cos., Inc. and Amherst College.
She received her undergraduate degree from Amherst College and a graduate degree from Columbia Law School.



